---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Gnosia">
  <h2>I love Gnosia</h2>

  <p>
    Gnosia is such a special game to me. The two most important characters
    (Setsu and Raqio) are both nonbinary, and the player character can be too. I
    played this game before I came out as nonbinary, and my repressed feelings
    intertwined with the fabulous art, music, and narrative to form a magical
    experience.
  </p>

  <h2>Raqio</h2>

  <p>Official art of Raqio from Gnosia.</p>

  <div class="photo-grid">
    <figure>
      <img
        data-aspect="square"
        src="/shrines/gnosia/assets/raqio1.webp"
        loading="lazy"
        width="1000"
        height="563"
      />
    </figure>
    <figure>
      <img
        src="/shrines/gnosia/assets/raqio2.webp"
        loading="lazy"
        width="800"
        height="800"
      />
    </figure>
    <figure>
      <img
        src="/shrines/gnosia/assets/raqio3.webp"
        loading="lazy"
        width="1000"
        height="1000"
      />
    </figure>
    <figure>
      <img
        src="/shrines/gnosia/assets/raqio4.webp"
        loading="lazy"
        width="1000"
        height="1000"
      />
    </figure>
    <figure>
      <img
        src="/shrines/gnosia/assets/raqio5.webp"
        loading="lazy"
        width="1000"
        height="1000"
      />
    </figure>
    <figure>
      <img
        data-aspect="square"
        data-position="top"
        src="/shrines/gnosia/assets/raqio6.webp"
        loading="lazy"
        width="600"
        height="1000"
      />
    </figure>
  </div>

  <h2>Commissioned art</h2>

  <p>
    I commissioned one of my favorite artists,{" "}
    <a href="https://sproutsnout.com/">sproutsnout</a>, to draw Raqio.
  </p>

  <div class="photo-grid">
    <figure>
      <img
        src="/shrines/gnosia/assets/sproutsnout/raqio.webp"
        alt=""
        loading="lazy"
        width="637"
        height="824"
      />
      <figcaption>Raqio</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
